freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Last night about 6 hours after receiving the shot I had itching and swelling around my right eye, which is still visible today although the itching has stopped. Then about 24 hours after receiving the shot I had hives inside my right elbow. Not sure if either of these things are related to the shot, but thought I should report them.
